Invocation Name: fine foraging
des: Get easy recipe suggestions to use with ingredients you can find at the farmer's market or even your own backyard! Including, sustainable, foraged foods is a simple and delicious way to upgrade your diet while lowering your environmental impact. There are original recipes for every meal and a few fun snacks all available from nature's pantry. Always be sure to forage responsibly and safely!
